        "content_zTdHHL": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where we ship",
            "content": "<p>We currently ship anywhere in the contiguous United States. We’re working on Alaska, Hawaii, and international shipping. If you’d like to be notified when we expand, drop your address into our waitlist on the homepage.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_LA3bgx": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping options and costs",
            "content": "<p>We keep this simple:</p><ul><li><strong>Standard shipping (3–5 business days)</strong> — [$X] flat rate, free on orders over [$Y] and on every subscription order.</li><li><strong>Expedited shipping (2 business days)</strong> — [$X] flat rate, available at checkout.</li></ul><p><em>*Drafting note: Replace bracketed amounts with the rates Zaid’s team configures in Shopify. Free shipping for subscriptions is recommended given subscription is the business model — confirm with finance before going live.</em></p><p>Orders ship Monday through Friday, excluding U.S. holidays. Orders placed after 12:00 PM PT typically ship the next business day.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_hzgdaE": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Tracking",
            "content": "<p>Once your order ships, you’ll get an email with a tracking link. You can also see tracking information in your account.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_CDWMTQ": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Subscriptions",
            "content": "<p>Subscription orders ship at the cadence you choose — every 30 days for the 30/month plan, every 30 days (with four 15-packs) for the 60/month plan. We send a reminder email a few days before each shipment so you can skip, swap, or update your address. Changes need to be made before the renewal processes.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_jPBq6a": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "If something goes wrong in transit",
            "content": "<p>Once a package leaves us, the carrier owns it. That said, we’re not going to leave you hanging if it gets lost or arrives damaged. Email hello@tonique.com within 14 days of the delivery date with your order number and a photo (for damage), and we’ll replace the order or refund you.</p><p>Two notes:</p><ul><li>If tracking shows your package was delivered but you can’t find it, please check with neighbors and your building first, then file a claim with the carrier. We’re happy to help, but stolen-from-porch claims need to start with the carrier.</li><li>If an address is entered incorrectly and the package is returned to us, we’ll reach out to confirm the correct address. Reshipping costs may apply.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "content_wXA4En": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Returns and refunds",
            "content": "<p>Tonique is a consumable supplement, which means we can’t resell returned product even if it’s unopened — that’s a food-safety standard, not a stinginess thing.</p><p>Here’s how we handle it:</p><ul><li><strong>Unopened orders</strong> — If you change your mind within 14 days of delivery and the box hasn’t been opened, email us. We’ll refund your purchase. You don’t need to ship the product back; please donate it or pass it along to a friend.</li><li><strong>Opened orders</strong> — If you tried it and it’s not for you, email us within 30 days of delivery. We offer a one-time satisfaction refund on your first order. Tell us what didn’t work — we read every note and it shapes the brand.</li><li><strong>Defective or damaged product</strong> — Always covered. Email us with a photo and we’ll make it right.</li></ul><p>Refunds are issued to the original payment method and typically appear within 5–10 business days, depending on your bank.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_dbDCwD": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Cancelling or pausing a subscription",
            "content": "<p>You can manage your subscription from your account page — skip a shipment, change your cadence, swap your address, or cancel. There are no cancellation fees and no calls required. If you’re having trouble, email hello@tonique.com and we’ll handle it for you.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_BwmAHk": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Questions",
            "content": "<p>Email <a href=\"mailto:hello@tonique.com\" title=\"mailto:hello@tonique.com\">hello@tonique.com</a>. We typically reply within one business day.</p>"
          }
        }
